nodes.text: A kybo was an organic airship manufactured by Zonama Sekot Shipbuilders. When Luke Skywalker, Mara Jade Skywalker and other Jedi arrived in Zonama Sekot for the first time, they were escorted by a flight of Ferroans piloting kyboes.

The ship resembled a huge manta ray with a single bullet-shaped gondola with two bone-colored fans protruding from the rear. Each kybo could be anchored to gnarled roots protruding from the Zonama Sekot surface by five slender lines. The ships were roughly three times the size of a YT-1300 freighter.
